|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([UserID@0, SearchPhrase@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                                 |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[UserID@0 as UserID, SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))]                         |
